<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About | Game Title</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/assets/profileimages/default.png">
    <script src="/js/tailwind.js"></script>
</head>
<%- include('partials/header') %>
<body class="bg-primary flex flex-col items-center">

    <div class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center p-8 w-screen lg:w-1/2  text-md">
        <!-- Author Section -->
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row w-full">
            <div class="flex flex-col">
                <p class="text-white text-xl m-4 font-bold">Author</p>
                <p class="text-white my-4">Hi, Im Cole Chiodo. A recent Computer Science Graduate with an interest in video games.<br/>Learn more on my <a href="http://colechiodo.cc" class="underline">personal site</a>.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    
        <!-- Project Description Section -->
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row w-full">
            <div class="flex flex-col">
                <p class="text-white text-xl m-4 font-bold">Project Description</p>
                <p class="text-white my-4">I decided to make this project while searching for a job to pass the time and improve my Software Engineering skills.</p>
                <p class="text-white my-4">{Game Title} is a turn based pvp strategy tactics game inspired by games such as:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-white mx-16">
                    <li class="mb-2">Fire Emblem</li>
                    <li class="mb-2">Advance Wars</li>
                    <li class="mb-2">Civilization</li>
                    <li class="mb-2">Final Fantasy Tactics</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    
        <!-- How It Is Made Section -->
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row w-full">
            <div class="flex flex-col">
                <p class="text-white text-xl m-4 font-bold">How I Made It</p>
                <p class="text-white my-4">{Project Name} was created using a combination of tools and technologies, including:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-white mx-16">
                    <li class="mb-2">Node and Express backend using TypeScript</li>
                    <li class="mb-2">NoSQL database to store user account information and sessions</li>
                    <li class="mb-2">Client side rendering with HTML canvas element using TypeScript</li>
                    <li class="mb-2">Client-Server communication using WebSockets</li>
                    <li class="mb-2">Pixel Art made using Aseprite, Tiled to create the game maps</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    
        <!-- Future Plans Section -->
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row w-full">
            <div class="flex flex-col">
                <p class="text-white text-xl m-4 font-bold">Future Plans</p>
                <p class="text-white my-4">Looking ahead, I plan to continue working on this project incrementally. Some of the key developments I would like to include are:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-white mx-16">
                    <li class="mb-2">Account Levels</li>
                    <li class="mb-2">Ranked Mode</li>
                    <li class="mb-2">Save Match History</li>
                    <li class="mb-2">Google/etc. OAuth</li>
                    <li class="mb-2">Profile Cosmetics</li>
                    <li class="mb-2">Alternate Units</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="text-white my-4">Stay tuned for updates!</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Credits Section -->
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row w-full">
            <div class="flex flex-col">
                <p class="text-white text-xl m-4 font-bold">Credits</p>
                <p class="text-white my-4">Font: "VT323" by The VT323 Project Authors (peter.hull@oikoi.com) is used under the  SIL Open Font License, Version 1.1.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    

</body>
<%- include('partials/footer') %>
</html>